cwe_description: The product reads data past the end, or before the beginning, of an intended buffer.
explanation: The function accesses table->key_info[key_number] without performing any bounds checking on the key_number parameter. If key_number is controlled by an attacker or can exceed the allocated size of the key_info array, this will result in an out-of-bounds read, potentially leading to information disclosure, denial of service, or other undefined behavior.
